OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784567930
OL,3,CNatural history museum finishes its
OL,4,Clargest ever redisplay project
OL,6,FA museum in Oxford has completed the
OL,7,Fbiggest redisplay project its ever
OL,8,Fundertaken in its 166-year history.
OL,10,FThe Oxford University Museum of
OL,11,FNatural History has been reimagined
OL,12,Fwith 48 new installations and displays.
OL,14,FThat includes the Megalosaurus, which
OL,15,Fwas discovered in an Oxfordshire
OL,16,Fquarry in Stonesfield, in the late
OL,17,F18th century.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
