CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784567930
OL,3,CNatural history museum finishes its
OL,4,Clargest ever redisplay project
OL,6,FThe project - called 'Life, as we know
OL,7,Fit' - brings together "thousands of
OL,8,Fspecimens to tell some of the most
OL,9,Fimportant stories in science",
OL,10,Faccording to the museum's director,
OL,11,FGavin Svenson.
OL,13,FMegalosaurus - which was the first
OL,14,Fdinosaur to ever be scientifically
OL,15,Fnamed - will be showcased alongside
OL,16,Fthe the predatory Eustreptospondylus
OL,17,Fand Cumnoria.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
